  m_Name: LeaveSuits
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  defaultText: 'Oh my... we''ve been friends so long, I didn''t realize you had these
    kind of EELings for me! If you''d really want me to move in... I''m not sure
    what to say... let''s... find the blankets while I think!  '
