      changesPhase: 0
      newPhase: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    blockedFlags: []
    usePhaseRequirement: 0
    requiredPhase: 0
  - optionText: Then don't say anything... we can just focus on how we feel about
      each other! And we can do the talking later.
